<div class="jumbotron">
	<% if current_user %>
	<h1>Hi again!</h1>
	<p>Take a quiz or check your progress</p>
	<%= link_to "Take a quiz!", quizzes_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %>
	<%= link_to "Check stats", user_path(current_user), class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %>
	<% else %>
	<h1>Welcome to Wordy</h1>
	<p>Practice your English -- with real Language!</p>
	<%= link_to "Sign up", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %>
	<% end %>
	<p> How it works:
		Give us a list of words you want to study<br />
		 (or choose from some pre-defined ones!)<br />
		Choose a quiz type:<br />
		 (multiple choice, matching, unscramble)<br />
		Practice with real examples -- straight from native texts, newspapers and other authentic sources!<br />
		Track your results!
	</p>
